title: Excel Learning Plan
description:
Excel Learning Plan

Duration: 57m| Video: AVC (.MP4) 1280x720 10fps | Audio: AAC 44.1KHz 2ch | 146MB
Genre: eLearning | Language: English

A quick course that will help you manage your classes better, prepare for exams in advance and plan your learning
What are the requirements?
Have Excel ready and you're good to go! Be sure not to forget about your classes and exams
What am I going to get from this course?
Over 8 lectures and 57 mins of content!
Create your first Excel learning and exam schedule
Use your newly made schedule to pace your learning to your own rythm and prepare in advance for your exams
What is the target audience?
Students everywhere should take this course and, of course, everyone that wants to learn the basics and also some advance stuff in Excel
